label: Westfield Republican
title: Westfield_Republican
exrest: The Westfield Republican is an American, English language newspaper providing news and information on the town and village of Westfield, as well as northern Chautauqua County in the state of New York. It began with the April 25, 1855 issue. The paper is currently published weekly. The paper claims to be the "First Republican paper printed in the USA."
